{
  "texts": [
    "To summarize, sharing and releasing foreign object datasets for railroad transmission lines is crucial for constructing foreign object detection models.",
    "By using this dataset for model training, foreign objects can be detected more efficiently, which will promote the development of artificial intelligence technology in the railway field.",
    "In this paper, we create a comprehensive and diverse dataset named \"RailFOD23\" specifically designed for foreign object detection on railway transmission lines.",
    "RailFOD23 comprises a total of 14,615 high-resolution images, making it a valuable resource for training and evaluating foreign object detection models in the railway domain.",
    "The main contributions of this paper are as follows:"
  ]
}